Call of Cthulhu - Cults Update
====================
Version: 1.19.0.3
Updated: 09-22-2018
Description: Right click a character with sanity loss for an option to restore sanity at the cost of suffering a mental break.\nSanity loss should now properly disappear after a time.\nFixed settings menu issue.\nStatues now calculated with reports.
====================

Download now on...
- Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/posts/cults-for-b19-0-21061032
- GitHub: https://github.com/Rim-Of-Madness-Team/Call-of-Cthulhu---Cults
- Steam: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=815039373
Discuss the mod on...
- Discord: https://discord.gg/AaVFA7V
- Ludeon forums: https://ludeon.com/forums/index.php?topic=26078.0

